Find Your Perfect Home in Kathmandu

No brokers, no hidden fees. Connect directly with property owners.

Why Choose No-Broker Kathmandu?

We're revolutionizing the rental market in Kathmandu

No Broker Fees

Save thousands on broker commissions. Connect directly with property owners.

Verified Properties

All properties are verified with SafeRent certification for your peace of mind.

Smart Search

AI-powered recommendations help you find properties that match your preferences.

How It Works

Simple steps to find your perfect home

Search

Browse verified properties with detailed filters and photos

2

Schedule Visit

Connect

Meet the owner, ask questions, and negotiate terms directly

4

Rent

Sign digital agreements and move in without any broker hassle

{/* CTA Section */}

Ready to Find Your Perfect Home?

Join thousands of happy tenants and property owners in Kathmandu

Get Started Today View Properties
